<template>
  <transition-group name="posts-list">
    <post-card
        v-for="(post,key) in posts"

        :key="key"

        :title="post.title"

        :description="post.description"

        :main-content="post.mainContent"
    />
  </transition-group>
</template>

<script>
import PostCardTitle from "@/components/PostCardTitle.vue";
export default {
  components:{
    PostCardTitle
  },
  posts:{
    type:Array,
    required: true
  }
}
</script>

<style lang="scss" scoped>

</style>
